Package org.apache.xpath.types

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ForEachGroupCompositeGroupingKey
    An object instance of this class, represents xsl:for-each-group instruction's run-time value of a composite grouping key for a particular group that is formed while evaluating xsl:for-each-group instruction.
    StringWithCollation
    An object of this class, supports implementation of xsl:for-each-group instruction's attribute 'collation'.
